AfriForum wants the EFF and its leaders to apologise publicly and pay for damages That’s for singing the anti-apartheid song "Dubul' ibhunu", which translates to "shoot the boer", on various occasions. AfriForum is bringing a civil case against the EFF in court today. JOHANNESBURG - Lobby group AfriForum is once again taking on Julius Malema about the singing of ‘Shoot the Boer’.